column1: Reviewed in the United States on August 27, 2024
column6: A great mug, it's not the first one I've had from Stanley. I am absolutely delighted with the product itself. Unfortunately, the cup I received was no longer new and was already damaged. It is a shame to receive a damaged product for such a price.
